<li>Don’t hesitate to reach out if you need to talk, cry, or just be silent together.</li>
<li>Your friendship means the world to me, and I'm here for you through this.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace.</li>
<li>Please know that you are not alone in your grief.</li>
